<content>
    <centered line="1"> Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</centered>
    <nikaya line="2">Abhidhammapiṭake</nikaya>
    <book line="3">Pañcapakaraṇa-aṭṭhakathā</book>
    <chapter line="4">Dhātukathā-aṭṭhakathā</chapter>
    <gatha1 line="5">Aṭṭhārasahi <pageBreak edition="Pali Text Society" number="0.0114" /><pageBreak edition="Myanmar" number="0.0001" /><pageBreak edition="Vipassana Research Institut" number="0.0001" /> bhedehi, vibhaṅgaṃ mārabhañjano;</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="6">Desayitvā mahāvīro, yaṃ tasseva anantaraṃ.</gathalast>
    <gatha1 line="7">Adesayi dhātukathaṃ, dhātubhedappakāsano;</gatha1>
    <gathalast line="8">Tassatthaṃ dīpayissāmi, taṃ suṇātha samāhitāti.</gathalast>
